---
---

<section class="wpi-conexao">
  <h2 class="wpi-conexao__headline">
    <span class="wpi-conexao__headline--white">Seguimos </span><span class="wpi-conexao__headline--gradient">100% independentes.</span>
  </h2>

  <div class="wpi-conexao__bottom">
    <div class="wpi-conexao__left">
      <div class="wpi-conexao__stats">
        <div class="wpi-conexao__stat">
          <p class="wpi-conexao__stat-label">mas conectados a mais de</p>
          <p class="wpi-conexao__stat-value wpi-conexao__stat-value--orange">90 agências</p>
        </div>
        <div class="wpi-conexao__stat">
          <p class="wpi-conexao__stat-label">em mais de</p>
          <p class="wpi-conexao__stat-value wpi-conexao__stat-value--blue">50 países</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="wpi-conexao__body">
        Compartilhando inteligência<br>de mercado, tecnologias<br>e estratégias.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="wpi-conexao__right">
      <img src="/images/wpi/world-map.png" alt="Mapa de conexões globais" class="wpi-conexao__map" />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .wpi-conexao {
    background: #0d0d0d;
    width: 100%;
    padding: 100px 165px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 48px;
  }

  .wpi-conexao__bottom {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 60px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .wpi-conexao__left {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 32px;
  }

  /* Headline */
  .wpi-conexao__headline {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 8.33vw, 7.5rem);
    line-height: 0.96;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .wpi-conexao__headline--white {
    color: #fff;
  }

  .wpi-conexao__headline--gradient {
    background: linear-gradient(-63.74deg, #ea0e81 4.82%, #a343cb 49.11%, #216ef2 93.39%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }

  /* Stats column */
  .wpi-conexao__stats {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 16px;
  }

  .wpi-conexao__stat {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0;
  }

  .wpi-conexao__stat-label {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(1.2rem, 3.1vw, 2.795rem);
    color: #fff;
    line-height: 1;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .wpi-conexao__stat-value {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 7.22vw, 6.5rem);
    line-height: 0.96;
    margin: 0;
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }

  .wpi-conexao__stat-value--orange {
    background-image: linear-gradient(90deg, #781e87 0%, #781e87 20%, #bf1b91 44.23%, #f28900 85%, #f3a400 89%, #f5bf00 93%, #f6d000 97%, #f7d600 100%);
  }

  .wpi-conexao__stat-value--blue {
    background-image: linear-gradient(-83.09deg, #ea0e81 4.82%, #a343cb 26.54%, #216ef2 66.14%, #253ead 80.19%, #6789d9 93.39%);
  }

  /* Body text */
  .wpi-conexao__body {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 2.39vw, 2.15rem);
    color: #fff;
    line-height: 1.4;
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* Map */
  .wpi-conexao__right {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .wpi-conexao__map {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
  }
</style>
